# LeafGuard AI — Training Pipeline: Tree → Individual Leaf → Train → Predict

## Problem

Your professor requires:
1. **Training**: Upload whole plant/tree images → auto-segment into individual leaves → train a classifier on those leaves → 100% confidence on training data
2. **Testing**: Upload new whole tree images → auto-segment → classify each leaf → >70% confidence required
3. The website must handle both workflows end-to-end

